text: Naomi Ellen Watts (born 28 September 1968) is an English actress. She played Rachel Keller in the horror movie The Ring (2002) and Ann Darrow in King Kong (2005). == Personal life == On June 9, 2023, Watts married actor Billy Crudup. == Notable roles == King Kong (2005) Ann Darrow The Impossible (2012) Maria Bennett The Ring Two (2005) Rachel Keller I Heart Huckabees (2004) Dawn Campbell 21 Grams (2003) Cristina Peck Ned Kelly (2003) Julia Cook The Ring (2002) Rachel Keller Mulholland Drive (2001) Betty Elms / Diane Selwyn Tank Girl (1995) Jet Girl Gross Misconduct (1993) Jennifer Carter == References == == Other websites == * Category:1968 births Category:Actors from Kent Category:English movie actors Category:English movie producers Category:English television actors Category:English voice actors Category:Living people
